description: Maruti Suzuki has delivered quality for years and this car is no exception. This Maruti Suzuki 800 Year 2011  has travelled a total of 72000km and features a Manual transmission system as well as other great features. Priced at Rs.1250000, this car is fantastic value for money. Or 500,000 to hand + 27300*43 lease to be continued. Can be seen at Minuwangoda
name: Maruti Suzuki 800  2011
